Attempt unauthorized actions

9Ô∏è‚É£ Learning Outcome (Day 18 Takeaway)

If an attacker can intercept and modify requests, they can control your application unless strong server-side security exists.

You clearly learned:

How attackers think

How HTTP manipulation works

Why API security is critical

Why frontend security alone is useless
